@startuml
[*] --> CreateAccount
CreateAccount --> AccountCreated : User creates account
AccountCreated --> WatchVideos : User watches videos
WatchVideos --> VideoWatched : User finishes watching a video
VideoWatched --> SaveVideo : User saves video in likes list
SaveVideo --> LikesListSaved : Video saved successfully
LikesListSaved --> ViewSavedVideos : User views saved videos from likes list
ViewSavedVideos --> DiscussionEntry : User enters discussion option
DiscussionEntry --> End : User ends session

@enduml
